videos.description: Trayce Jackson-Davis gets the pass from Trey Galloway and slams it down with his left hand plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jackson-Davis amped after early and-1 slam) 2020/12/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jackson-Davis amped after early and-1 slam

videos.description: Armaan Franklin records the block on defense, then Indiana gets out in transition and Race Thompson hammers it down on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Indiana gets denial on one end, then Thompson dunks it hard on the other) 2020/12/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Indiana gets denial on one end, then Thompson dunks it hard on the other

videos.description: Indiana runs the inbounds play to perfection as Khristian Lander lobs the ball up to Trayce Jackson-Davis for the emphatic dunk.
